%%{init: {'theme': 'default', 'themeVariables': {'fontSize': '16px'}}}%%
flowchart TB
    A[1. gh run list\nfind latest failure] --> B[2. Check HEAD\nvs failed SHA]
    B --> C[3. gh run view --log-failed\nfetch failure logs]
    C --> D[4. Classify]
    D --> E[fmt:\ncargo fmt]
    D --> F[clippy:\nfix each lint]
    D --> G[compile:\nfix each error]
    D --> H[test:\nfix impl or expectation]
    D --> I[other:\nopen GitHub issue]
    E & F & G & H --> J[Verify:\ncargo check / test]
    J --> K[passes:\ngit push]
    J --> L[fails:\nopen GitHub issue]

    style I fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style L fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style K fill:#27ae60,color:#fff
